sand_witch: "Ah, traveler... Look at your boat. So practical. So... hideously gray. You need style. You need my Golden Hull upgrade. Only 100 gold pieces!"
- Buy the Golden Hull (-100 Gold)
	set {gold} -= 100.0
	sand_witch: "A splendid choice! It shines so brightly... active your inner glory, tiny captain!"
- Leave her cave
	sand_witch: "Suit yourself, dull traveler. Stay gray. Stay forgotten."